          "evidence_text_excerpt": "What are the fees for the BMO Savings Amplifier Account?\nThe Savings Amplifier Account includes a $0 monthly plan fee, a $0 minimum opening deposit, and no fees on any self-serve transfers to your other BMO accounts. A $5 fee applies for each pre-authorized debit, cash withdrawals, and transfers made in branch or with a Telephone Banking associate.\nWhat type of savings accounts does BMO offer? BMO offers several savings accounts, including: Savings Amplifier: Earn a competitive interest rate and get unlimited self-serve transfers with no monthly fees. You can earn a promotional\u00a0interest rate * when you open a Savings Amplifier Account and a BMO chequing account. Premium Rate Savings: Open this account together with a BMO chequing account under the same plan. Earn daily interest on every dollar. Transaction fees vary depending on the plan you choose. U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings:",
