          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-c33b96039e1d070b",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "What are the transaction limits of a U.S. Dollar Premium Savings Account?\nThis will depend on the bank Plan for the BMO chequing account that you have. Transaction limits are shared among these two accounts.\nWhat type of savings accounts does BMO offer? BMO offers several savings accounts, including: Savings Amplifier: Earn a competitive interest rate and get unlimited self-serve transfers with no monthly fees. You can earn a promotional interest rate * when you open a Savings Amplifier Account and a BMO chequing account. Savings Builder: Get a base interest rate each month to maximize your savings and one debit transaction per month, at no cost. *23 You can earn additional interest when you increase your monthly balance by at least $200 each month. U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings: Open this account together with a BMO chequing account under the same plan. Save in U.S. dollars and earn",
