          "evidence_text_excerpt": "U.S Dollar Premium Rate Savings Account FAQs\nWhat is a U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings Account? A U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings Account functions like a regular savings account where you can store your money and earn interest, but with added perks. BMO\u2019s U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings Account is a good savings option for frequent travellers to the U.S. that want to save and earn interest on their U.S. money. You get the flexibility and convenience of accessing your money whenever you need it. Plus, it can be paired with any BMO chequing account, so you only pay one monthly account fee.",
